    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10517560>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1–15. Ovipennis spp.: adults. Depositories of the specimens: 1 in IZCAS; 2, 3 and 11 in CHSY; 4 in WIGJ (ex CAV); 5, 8 and 14 in CKC; 6 in CAV; 7, 13 and 15 in MWM/ZSM (7 ex CKC); 9 and 12 in NHMUK (©The Trustees of NHMUK); 10 in SCAU (ex CHSY)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10517560/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10517562>
    dc:description "FIGURES 16–19. Male genitalia of Ovipennis spp. Depositories of the specimens dissected: 16 in CHSY; 17 in SCAU; 18 in WIGJ (ex CAV); 19 in CAV." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10517562/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10517566>
    dc:description "FIGURES 24–29. Female genitalia of Ovipennis spp. Depositories of the specimens dissected: 24 and 29 in CHSY; 25, 27 and 28 in CKC; 26 in CAV." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10517566/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10517570>
    dc:description "FIGURES 33–38. Live adults (Figs 33–37) and habitat (Fig. 38) of Ovipennis spp. 33 and 34, O. bicolora, China, Mt. Omei (photo by Si-Yao Huang); 35 and 36, O. regina sp. n., China, Yunnan (photo by Hong-wei Zhang); 37, O. hanae sp. n., China, Yunnan (photo by Hong-wei Zhang); 38, Qingyinge, Mt. Emei, Sichuan, the habitat in the type locality of O. bicolora." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10517570/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

